data.name: Vorpall, the Sickle-Fanged
data.notes: "Vorpall, the Sickle-Fanged" resides within banshee cave the entrance of which is guarded by two oc-servs to the north west of Anvil Sandplain in northern Sylvalum. From the entrance simply take a right followed by a left to find Vorpall near a large group of Crystal Blatta on the floor (may take a moment for Vorpall to load in).
